for minority Alawites can be head of that

17:21.807 --> 17:25.278 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
government, so they think you'll eventually
get to that point and the Russians have signaled

17:25.311 --> 17:30.549 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the United States they're not so much wedded
to Assad as the idea of a unitary state.

17:30.583 --> 17:36.522 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So the steps are a very, very tall order,
