measure whether someone is on a course they

22:54.273 --> 22:56.208 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
believe in and they're going to stick with?

22:56.242 --> 23:01.146 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SHIELDS: Well, I mean, he was caught, Judy,
the president was caught on the red line,

23:01.180 --> 23:02.348 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
