people sad or devastated or disappointed?

48:04.782 --> 48:10.621 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FELLOWES: I adore these questions because
they're always asked in such optimism, as

48:10.654 --> 48:16.961 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
