are other things that will make them happy.

48:22.700 --> 48:25.803 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And Maggie will say some things that I hope
will make them laugh.

48:25.836 --> 48:29.340 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOODRUFF: What should fans expect, the audience
expect?

48:29.373 --> 48:36.247 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MCGOVERN: I would say that the audience will
feel satisfied that they've had a chance to

48:36.280 --> 48:46.457 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
