way. I think they'll feel full and not shortchanged.

48:46.490 --> 48:52.296 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FELLOWES: It's enough for me that people
enjoyed it, and they had a thing on Sunday

48:52.329 --> 48:56.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
