the next day, that's enough of an achievement

49:06.710 --> 49:11.982 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
for me. I don't need to feel that the world
will never be the same again after "Downton,"

49:12.016 --> 49:15.085 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
