50:33.831 --> 50:37.434 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MALIK COLE: I feel like I'm hurting, I'm
dying.

50:37.468 --> 50:43.707 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOODRUFF: As the weather turned colder in
late October, Malik's condition became unmanageable.

50:43.741 --> 50:49.513 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
His parents reluctantly decided to turn the
children over to Child Protective Services

50:49.546 --> 50:55.853 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
