years. They will then have the option to buy

51:15.773 --> 51:17.474 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the house.

51:17.508 --> 51:22.980 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The deal also comes with financial and educational
training for the parents, tutoring for the

51:23.013 --> 51:27.484 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
kids, and a fully-stocked kitchen just in
time for Christmas.

51:27.518 --> 51:28.819 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
